<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="put-up-with">put up with</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-tolerate">1.<strong>忍受；容忍 (tolerate)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can’t put up with their smoking any longer. 
我再也无法忍受他们抽烟了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can put up with many things, but not with people who steal.
我能容忍很多事情，但绝不容忍小偷小摸的人。</p></div></div>